  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620050/extras/ddc95fba5c75e5468705c2669f7505ba.avif?t=1734851518\" width=600 height=322 /></span><br><br>The sole survivor stages of death are a whole new game; there are so many ways to kill yourself.<br><br><br>In single-player mode, you can play three temples with different stages; every stage has its own way of killing.<br>Show your gaming skills and defeat all the traps.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620050/extras/686db965194b34ec32016f1631a6cecc.poster.avif?t=1734851518\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620050/extras/686db965194b34ec32016f1631a6cecc.webm?t=1734851518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620050/extras/686db965194b34ec32016f1631a6cecc.mp4?t=1734851518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In multiplayer mode, play with your buddies and choose a team between Aztec and Mayan. Collect coins and don't drop until the time runs out.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620050/extras/b8b32cd46f0a1ef1bdbb4e028aff987f.avif?t=1734851518\" width=600 height=322 /></span><br><br>Sandbox has a grid-based system and more than 20 traps, show creativity to build undefeated maps.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620050/extras/5b268217c1ca90a8e21ce65019d8f19b.poster.avif?t=1734851518\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620050/extras/5b268217c1ca90a8e21ce65019d8f19b.webm?t=1734851518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620050/extras/5b268217c1ca90a8e21ce65019d8f19b.mp4?t=1734851518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620050/extras/ddc95fba5c75e5468705c2669f7505ba.avif?t=1734851518\" width=600 height=322 /></span><br><br>The sole survivor stages of death are a whole new game; there are so many ways to kill yourself.<br><br><br>In single-player mode, you can play three temples with different stages; every stage has its own way of killing.<br>Show your gaming skills and defeat all the traps.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620050/extras/686db965194b34ec32016f1631a6cecc.poster.avif?t=1734851518\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620050/extras/686db965194b34ec32016f1631a6cecc.webm?t=1734851518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620050/extras/686db965194b34ec32016f1631a6cecc.mp4?t=1734851518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In multiplayer mode, play with your buddies and choose a team between Aztec and Mayan. Collect coins and don't drop until the time runs out.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620050/extras/b8b32cd46f0a1ef1bdbb4e028aff987f.avif?t=1734851518\" width=600 height=322 /></span><br><br>Sandbox has a grid-based system and more than 20 traps, show creativity to build undefeated maps.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620050/extras/5b268217c1ca90a8e21ce65019d8f19b.poster.avif?t=1734851518\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620050/extras/5b268217c1